Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//TEXT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.53,0:02:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.05,0:02:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是我的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明和我一樣是這個神社的女巫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.54,0:02:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明揮舞著禦神刀斬殺過「古物」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明應該是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.11,0:02:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我卻連母親大人的名字和長相都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.41,0:02:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.32,0:03:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不… 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這還真讓心興奮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:05:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是… 不能隨心所欲地行動還真讓人不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝也是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縱然失去了自由之身 果然肚子還是會餓的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要吃點東西了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是近來的食物都是些難以下嚥的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連約定都沒法遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如汝所知道的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 是曾經知道卻已忘卻的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子很餓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到想吃卻無法顧及是否難吃的地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類之子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.45,0:07:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何憤怒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝也要吞噬食物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 比起吾等所食之物更為怪異
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說為什麼的話 因為汝是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 得決定該獎勵你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你將約定遵守到最後的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該給你什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而如果你無法遵守約定到最後的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又該拿走什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是肚子餓了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可憐啊 現在就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦吧 背棄約定的人之傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.06,0:09:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去問唯芳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:10:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於你的… 真相
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是… 更衣小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是… 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是… 誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.26,0:11:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭還疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了 喝了咖啡清醒多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文人先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能…是有點餓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Guimauve」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 「Guimauve」原本就是紅色的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會根據混入的原料而導致顏色發生變化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 還是覺得這個顏色更符合小夜你的口味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜你很喜歡吧 紅色的和這種味道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜她醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說喝過咖啡後精神好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後我問了她還想吃點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說她想吃「Guimauve」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快吃點東西準備一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是個好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上的工作 圓滿完成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社庭院的打掃也完成得很乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人的臉色…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人究竟去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有給我留言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿校服了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不穿校服的話總覺得心裡不踏實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對現在的小夜來說或許是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.67,0:15:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為習慣了這工作 看來還是不能大意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是杯子什麼的摔破了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以來幫忙收拾的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了 已經都收拾好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文人先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筒鳥老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 更衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問要吃點什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真是難辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜你也吃點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只吃「Guimauve」的話不夠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我還要咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:17:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師你要喝點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不喝咖啡了 給我來杯原味的紅茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 聽說更衣同學家的神社有很多珍貴的書籍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍貴的書籍？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像古老的文獻這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說在倉庫裡堆著的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些書籍 能不能給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得問一下我的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親在家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話 我想今天就查閱一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天… 嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.97,0:17:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 今天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 我絕不會帶走裡面的任何東西 而且也會小心查閱的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是看看 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從以前開始就對古老的傳記和神話很有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過卻不太有機會過目真正的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇來到這個鎮上也是因為想見識真品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.92,0:18:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思啊 更衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬要你帶我進來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 我會和父親說明的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親還沒有回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:19:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人究竟去哪裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得這個怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像之前上課講鬼故事時提到的那個傳說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為其取名為「古物」的究竟是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 無論在哪本書上都沒有記載
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 就如那名字的字面意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.06,0:19:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自古以來確實是有吞噬人類的東西存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.92,0:19:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而唯一能打倒那些傢伙的東西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一能打倒那些傢伙的東西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禦神刀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 不好意思 剛才一直在發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 不過啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算玩這種愚蠢的遊戲到什麼時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了這本書你還沒察覺到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,察覺到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這紙… 是新的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明應該是記載了傳記的古書
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的書… 全都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 全都是假的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.44,0:21:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾諾同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈同學…
